title: High Plat Jungler LF Team
body:
I am currently plat 3, in promotions to plat 2. I have experience playing in teams of diamond calibre previously and my overall goal is to continue to grow as a player.

Comfortable on a variety of champs:
- Ekko
- Master Yi
- Sejuani
- Kha'Zix
- Kindred
- Graves
- Elise
- Lee Sin
- Nidalee
- Udyr
- Rengar
- Jax

If you are interested please feel free to add me in game: Satanic Chicken
